Raspberry Pi Instructions
################ MONGODB NOT SUPPORTED ON ARM THROUGH DOCKER #######################

Flash Hypriot Image onto SD
1. Follow directions from this site (Windows):
http://blog.hypriot.com/getting-started-with-docker-and-windows-on-the-raspberry-pi/

Boot Pi
1. After initialisation finishes, press any button and login
login: pirate
password: hypriot (maybe, check above website)

Pull NostalgiaDrive from github
1. Type below into the terminal (5 min)
git clone https://github.com/mchellmer/DockerMongoFceuxPython.git

Build NostalgiaDrive
1. Navigate to nd folder
cd DockerMongoFceuxPython/dockernd

2. Type the below in the terminal (30-90min)
docker-compose Build
